These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea
2 different pets are kept: snake, lizard
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, singing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, old-henry
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, emerald
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, thai
City: boston, nizza
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the siglo-smoker##8
3. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person who likes apricot##6
4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
5. the old-henry-smoker is not to the left of the person traveling to boston##8
6. the thai is not the person traveling to boston##6
7. the owner of the snake is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | coffee      |
| Pet          | lizard | snake   |
| Hobby         | singing    | board-games |
| Cigar           | siglo     | old-henry    |
| Color   | emerald    | apricot       |
| Nationality   | italian    | thai        |
| City     | boston     | nizza        |

